 care, however, the A-wing is one of the deadliest fighters in the skies.','A-wing1.jpg',NULL,'Source text CC-BY-SA 3.0 from http://d6holocron.com/wiki/A-wing','["http://d6holocron.com/wiki/A-wing"]',419,41736);
